[SPEAKER_03] all these things that we well know.

1111
01:31:06,239 --> 01:31:11,960
[SPEAKER_03] And then at that stage, there was the discretion of the national schemes would be much more limited.

1112
01:31:11,960 --> 01:31:17,100
[SPEAKER_03] There could be still some discretion because bank systems are very much a national affair,

1113
01:31:17,100 --> 01:31:19,600
[SPEAKER_03] and there's no one-size-fits-all for everybody.

1114
01:31:19,600 --> 01:31:22,300
[SPEAKER_03] But it would be mostly harmonized,

1115
01:31:22,300 --> 01:31:25,020
[SPEAKER_03] and the share of national discretion would be less,

1116
01:31:25,020 --> 01:31:28,220
[SPEAKER_03] whereas in the first stage, the reinsurance stage,

1117
01:31:28,220 --> 01:31:33,159
[SPEAKER_03] it would be much more a national approach with some degree of harmonization.

1118
01:31:33,159 --> 01:31:36,380
[SPEAKER_03] And so the weights between national and harmonized approach

1119
01:31:36,380 --> 01:31:38,460
[SPEAKER_03] kind of shift between these two phases.

1120
01:31:38,460 --> 01:31:40,020
[SPEAKER_04] Thank you.

1121
01:31:40,020 --> 01:31:45,180
[SPEAKER_04] Gospodine Odak, mi se natragu usklađivanja sa direktivom,

1122
