[SPEAKER_04] s naglaskom na fiscal backstop problem.

1187
01:36:48,819 --> 01:36:58,800
[SPEAKER_03] That's of course a fairly difficult question.

1188
01:36:58,800 --> 01:37:00,640
[SPEAKER_03] It's clear.

1189
01:37:00,640 --> 01:37:05,300
[SPEAKER_03] This is a political issue on the fiscal backstop

1190
01:37:05,300 --> 01:37:11,199
[SPEAKER_03] and the major question is,

1191
