1208
01:38:04,439 --> 01:38:07,920
[SPEAKER_03] other forms of financing outside bank credit

1209
01:38:07,920 --> 01:38:11,939
[SPEAKER_03] would be more readily used and accessible

1210
01:38:11,939 --> 01:38:14,739
[SPEAKER_03] certainly for small and medium-sized enterprises.

1211
01:38:14,739 --> 01:38:17,640
[SPEAKER_03] So all these issues move into the direction

1212
01:38:17,640 --> 01:38:23,439
[SPEAKER_03] to reduce the risk inherent in the banking system

1213
01:38:23,439 --> 01:38:25,279
[SPEAKER_03] as we have seen in the past.

1214
