[SPEAKER_03] there is some final backstop behind it.

1228
01:39:09,500 --> 01:39:11,779
[SPEAKER_03] And given the setup in EMU

1229
01:39:11,779 --> 01:39:13,560
[SPEAKER_03] where we have the independent central bank

1230
