1239
01:39:36,159 --> 01:39:38,039
[SPEAKER_03] You need some mechanism

1240
01:39:38,039 --> 01:39:39,880
[SPEAKER_03] which is capable of performing

1241
01:39:39,880 --> 01:39:42,300
